Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Grace  Morris
AuthorCountry: United Kingdom (Great Britain
Text: "Hey guys i'm Grace!\nI am the Owner & Creative Director of Wanderlust Grace\
  \ (my travel blog).\n I\u2019ve been working on my blog for a couple of months now\
  \ and hope to get it up and running in the next 2 weeks, eeek exciting!!\n\nI'm\
  \ 20 years old and in june 2018 I quit my job and started my solo world trip. I\
  \ moved from a small country town in Australia and decided to travel Europe for\
  \ 3 months before settling down for an icy cold winter in London.\n\nAmongst my\
  \ travels I\u2019ve covered, Italy, France, Austria, Czech Republic, Spain, Germany,\
  \ Norway, Greece, Croatia, USA and so many more incredible places.\n\nTravel is\
  \ the absolute love of my life hence the reason I had to leave my two year old puppy\
  \ at home.. I know heartbreaking !!!\n\nLong story short I have so many amazing\
  \ stories and pictures to show and tell and I cannot wait to share with you all\
  \ and hopefully inspire others to take the leap and Travel.\n\nLove, Grace xo"
